quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  54,23,"Samuud deqsita mari sinni Nabii Saalic dirabboyseeniih, wohul farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  54,24,"Tokkel nek numuk teynah yan inki seehadaytu kataynaa iyyen? Diggah, nanu toysa makoo (maxqawit) kee cabut nan"
  54,25,"Nek fanaak wacyi kaal oobaa? aleey, takkem hinna usuk dirabli kaxxiina li iyyen"
  54,26,Beera digaala keenil obta waqdi aaxige lon addunyaa kee akeeral dirabli kaxxiina li kinni mara. (saalic kinnik ken kinnim)
  54,27,"Diggah, nanu usun esseren Alá xaxxaqak tet ayyaaqennooh keenih ruubenno mokkoroh, toysa digaala keenil obtam qambaalaay, ken adal isbir"
  54,28,"Kaadu Nabii Saalicow ku marah keenih waris diggah, lee ken kee Alâ fanal kurrumtaah, mariiy ayro keenik yaaqubeeh, kulli arakil le num geytimam"
  54,29,"Tokkel Sinni kataysah seeceenih Alá qidimih, edde luk usuk alá xabbaheeh qideh"
  54,30,Wohul anu ken digaalehik Yi digaalaa kee Yi meesisso mannak teneeh
  54,31,"Diggah Nanu jibriil keenil rubneeh, inki adda keenit xongoleeh inkih rabeenih, edde luk usun gaso li dagiiree kee bocoy buluulunteh inna yekken"
  54,32,"Kaadu nummah, Qhuraan kassiisih xabbacosnehik, tohul kaskassoowaah qakkaloowa mari maay yan"
  54,33,"Nabii Luut mari sinni Nabii luut meesissoosa dirabboyseeniih, wohul farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  54,34,"Diggah, Nanu xeet keenil rubne digaalah, Nabii Luut buxah mari (kaa kataate mara kinnuk) koh raaquh, nanu ken naggosneh woo digaalak maaci bar"
  54,35,"Ama asallam Ni xaquk yan niqmata, Tonnal galatna nee faatite mara"
  54,36,"kaadu nummah Nabii Luut Ni digaalay gibdil ken meesiiseeh, woo meesissoosat shakkiteeniih kaa dirabboyseenih"
  54,37,"Kaadu nummah Kay qibina kaa essereenih umaane edde faxoonuh, edde luk intiita ken waysisneeh, Yi digaalaa kee Yi meesisso tamannak tammoysa keenik inne"
  54,38,Kaadu nummah dabaqta digaalay salalta maaca keenil maacisse
  54,39,Yalli yi digaalaa kee meesisso tammoysa keenik iyye
  54,40,"Kaadu nummah, Qhuraan kassiisih xabbacosnehik, tohul kaskassoowaah qakkaloowa mari maay yan"